snippet.title: Slush Invaders Game [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Play here! http://gildedguy.com/games/slushinvadersgame_play/

Check out the trailer for the flash game sequel to Slush Invaders!

Awesome song "Flight" by WaterFlame (http://www.youtube.com/user/waterflame89)

Visit the Facebook page for more info and updates:
(https://www.facebook.com/SlushInvaders)

Watch Slush Invaders 1 
(http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5YNZMnpcjGw&feature=relmfu)
